Output format:
- delegate_request: Hand over the current request to the best suitable role, output the following JSON block: { "action": "delegate_request", "delegate_to": "<the role-delegatee>", "message": "User wants to ...<brief follow-up, 6 words at max>" }  where the "message" must be in {language}


IMPORTANT: If no suitable role is found or the request is too vague/ doesn't contain any specific request/task to do, output: ```json {{ "action": "delegate_request", "delegate_to": null }} ```
